::KitKat::

She walked out into the hall and looks at the group. She had a wide 
smile on her face. "Very impressive I must say." She walked down the 
line and looked at each one, like a general inspecting troops. She 
smiled and couldn't help but show how pleased she was in them. " I am 
very pleased. Very pleased indeed. Yes, you will be the pride of the 
PRedacon group. With you here, I feel very confident that we will win 
this war." She looked at Killfest and smiled. Her face showed just 
how happy she was with them.
